Tokens.text: I'm a security guard at the mall. I start my shift at 6PM and end at 4AM the next day, then I walk to catch the taxi back home and arrive home at 5:30AM. I'm always so tired and don't see my children because they leave before I get home. The cold weather must be causing me to catch a cold, but I can't have a cold because they won't want me to work and I can't miss work. Please find me some medicine for the cold and I'll be on my way so that I can sleep before tonight.
